I found the reason for java.lang.StackOverflowError with our (gmfgen) model if XMLResource.OPTION_DEFER_IDREF_RESOLUTION is set to TRUE:

XMLHelperImpl.setValue(...) is calling:
      {
        object.eSet(feature, value);
        break;
      }

for the feature which is not changeable in the model. As a result object.eSet() call cause infinite loop because corresponding 
"case GMFGenPackage.GEN_COMPARTMENT__NODE:" was not generated for not changeable feature..

This unchangeable feature is an "opposite" to another changeable (but not contaiment) one. The workaround: make "unchangeable" feature changeable. ;-)

Finally GMF editor works well.
